oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Young couple
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Young couple, in Edwardian dress, posed on a studio bench. He is holding a straw hat and she is holding a small book. He has on a polka dot bowtie and she has on an elaborate hat with feathers. A ring [engagement] is on her hand.
